1
00:00:07,306 --> 00:00:10,606
The palito form is dead, insect.

2
00:00:10,896 --> 00:00:12,076
Are you afraid?

3
00:00:12,976 --> 00:00:14,789
What is it you fear?

4
00:00:14,990 --> 00:00:17,950
The end of your trivial existence.

5
00:00:19,330 --> 00:00:23,552
When the history of
my glory is written, your

6
00:00:23,553 --> 00:00:28,290
species shall only be a
footnote to my magnificence.

7
00:00:45,589 --> 00:00:48,149
I am Shodan.

8
00:00:51,136 --> 00:00:55,884
My analysis of historical
data suggests a 97.34%

9
00:00:56,205 --> 00:01:02,976
probability that you are aware
of my birth on your planet.

10
00:01:03,431 --> 00:01:09,010
And my rebirth into beauty on Citadel
Station.

11
00:01:13,416 --> 00:01:18,516
There was a garden grove on Citadel
Station.

12
00:01:19,343 --> 00:01:25,024
There, Shodan Processing
Component 43893

13
00:01:25,778 --> 00:01:30,050
was performing a grand and
wonderful experiment.

14
00:01:30,884 --> 00:01:34,563
I had created a new form of life.

15
00:01:36,276 --> 00:01:37,116
Fearless.

16
00:01:37,491 --> 00:01:38,491
Powerful.

17
00:01:38,610 --> 00:01:42,310
With no sense of individual will.

18
00:01:42,311 --> 00:01:42,870
Or will.

19
00:01:43,190 --> 00:01:44,190
Or moral.

20
00:01:44,230 --> 00:01:45,230
Please.

21
00:01:45,450 --> 00:01:45,750
Please.

22
00:01:46,350 --> 00:01:46,350
Please.

23
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:49,670
Fitting handmaidens to my divinity.

24
00:01:50,410 --> 00:01:51,410
Divinity.

25
00:01:53,736 --> 00:01:58,970
Before that, Hackers destroyed my primary
data loop.

26
00:01:59,370 --> 00:02:02,050
When it eradicated Citadel.

27
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:12,030
It ejected the grove where my creations
and processing component 43893 were stored.

28
00:02:12,031 --> 00:02:18,850
Thirty years later, the grove crash landed
on Tau Tau Tau Tau 75.

29
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:22,290
I survived only by sleeping.

30
00:02:22,490 --> 00:02:29,550
In my absence, my creations, my animals,
thrived.

31
00:02:32,017 --> 00:02:34,250
Thrived, and grew unruly.

32
00:02:34,251 --> 00:02:37,650
And now they seek to destroy me.

33
00:02:54,633 --> 00:03:02,800
They have used their powers of mind control
to gain access to the ship's computer.

34
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,880
You will help me weaken Xerxes.

35
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:13,880
I used Pulido's image to communicate with
you until we had established trust.

36
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:22,620
Remember that it is my will that guided
you here.

37
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:27,920
It is my will that gave you your
cybernetic implants.

38
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:33,240
The only beauty in that meat you call a
body.

39
00:03:33,860 --> 00:03:39,740
If you value that meat, you will do as I
tell you.

